sync-labels.yml uses `target_repository` input (not `repo`)
## Context
The workflow accepts three inputs:
- `target_repository` (required): owner/repo format
- `dry_run` (optional, default: true): preview mode
- `allow_added_labels` (optional, default: true): preserve labels not in config

